data.name: grdSearchOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SLIP_CODE SLIP_CODE , B.SLIP_NAME SLIP_NAME , A.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE , A.HANGMOG_NAME HANGMOG_NAME , A.HOSP_CODE HOSP_CODE FROM OCS0102 B , OCS0103 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE AND A.HANGMOG_NAME_INX LIKE '%'||:f_search_word||'%' AND TO_DATE(:f_order_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND NVL(A.END_DATE, TO_DATE('99981231', 'YYYYMMDD')) AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.SLIP_CODE = A.SLIP_CODE ORDER BY A.SLIP_CODE, A.HANGMOG_CODE

data.name: grdSlipHangmog.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT C.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE, C.HANGMOG_NAME HANGMOG_NAME, C.ORDER_GUBUN ORDER_GUBUN, FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORDER_GUBUN_BAS', C.ORDER_GUBUN) ORDER_GUBUN_NAME, C.SPECIFIC_COMMENT FROM OCS0103 C WHERE C.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.ORDER_GUBUN IN ('I') AND C.SLIP_CODE LIKE :f_slip_code AND C.HANGMOG_NAME_INX LIKE :f_search_word AND :f_order_date BETWEEN C.START_DATE AND NVL(C.END_DATE, TO_DATE('99981231', 'YYYYMMDD')) ORDER BY 5, 2, 1

data.value: SELECT 'S' IOCS_GUBUN , A.FKOUT1001 , A.GROUP_SER , A.BOGYONG_CODE , C.BOGYONG_NAME , A.NALSU , A.EMERGENCY , A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN FROM OCS0303 A , OCS0142 B , DRG0120 C WHERE :f_order_mode = 1 AND A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE AND A.MEMB = :f_memb AND A.YAKSOK_CODE = :f_yaksok_code -- AND A.INPUT_GUBUN = :f_input_gubun AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.INPUT_TAB = :f_input_tab AND B.ORDER_GUBUN = SUBSTR(A.ORDER_GUBUN, 2, 1) AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+) = A.BOGYONG_CODE UNION ALL SELECT 'O' IO_GUBUN , A.FKOUT1001 , A.GROUP_SER , A.BOGYONG_CODE , C.BOGYONG_NAME , A.NALSU , A.EMERGENCY , A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN FROM OCS1003 A , OCS0142 B , DRG0120 C WHERE :f_order_mode = 2 AND A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE AND A.FKOUT1001 = :f_fk_in_out_key AND A.ORDER_DATE = :f_order_date AND A.INPUT_GUBUN = :f_input_gubun AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.INPUT_TAB = :f_input_tab AND B.ORDER_GUBUN = SUBSTR(A.ORDER_GUBUN, 2, 1) AND C.HOSP_CODE (+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+) = A.BOGYONG_CODE UNION ALL SELECT 'I' IO_GUBUN , A.FKINP1001 , A.GROUP_SER , A.BOGYONG_CODE , C.BOGYONG_NAME , A.NALSU , A.EMERGENCY , A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN FROM OCS2003 A , OCS0142 B , DRG0120 C WHERE :f_order_mode = 3 AND A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE AND A.FKINP1001 = :f_fk_in_out_key AND A.ORDER_DATE = :f_order_date AND A.INPUT_GUBUN = :f_input_gubun AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.INPUT_TAB = :f_input_tab AND B.ORDER_GUBUN = SUBSTR(A.ORDER_GUBUN, 2, 1) AND C.HOSP_CODE (+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+) = A.BOGYONG_CODE UNION ALL SELECT 'C' IO_GUBUN , A.FKOCS6010 , A.GROUP_SER , A.BOGYONG_CODE , C.BOGYONG_NAME , A.NALSU , A.EMERGENCY , A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN FROM OCS6013 A , OCS0142 B , DRG0120 C WHERE :f_order_mode = 4 AND A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE AND A.FKOCS6010 = :f_fk_in_out_key AND A.PLAN_ORDER_DATE = :f_order_date AND A.INPUT_GUBUN = :f_input_gubun AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.INPUT_TAB = :f_input_tab AND B.ORDER_GUBUN = SUBSTR(A.ORDER_GUBUN, 2, 1) AND C.HOSP_CODE (+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+) = A.BOGYONG_CODE ORDER BY 3 ASC;

data.name: laySlipCodeTree.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT D.SLIP_GUBUN , D.SLIP_GUBUN_NAME , C.SLIP_CODE , C.SLIP_NAME , D.SLIP_GUBUN || C.SLIP_CODE ORDERBYKEY FROM OCS0142 A , OCS0103 B , OCS0102 C , OCS0101 D WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE AND A.INPUT_TAB = '10' AND A.MAIN_YN = 'Y' AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.ORDER_GUBUN = A.ORDER_GUBUN AND C.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.SLIP_CODE = B.SLIP_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE = C.HOSP_CODE AND D.SLIP_GUBUN = C.SLIP_GUBUN ORDER BY 1 , ORDERBYKEY
